             was indicted for <rs id="t17930529-6-off27" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17930529-6-off27" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17930529-6-off27" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
