                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930529-6-off27 t17930529-6-cd28"></join>, eleven iron bars, value 16 s. an iron rail, value 4 s. the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17930529-6-victim123" type="victimName">
                           William Pardo 
                           Allet
                        <interp inst="t17930529-6-victim123" type="surname" value="Allet"></interp>
